timing_enable_...sewidth_checks(25.10)  timing_enable_...sewidth_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_enable_derating_for_pulsewidth_checks

Syntax
        timing_enable_derating_for_pulsewidth_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: false

       Controls  whether  the  cell  check  derates,  set by set_timing_derate
       -cell_check command, can be applied for pulse width checks.

       When set to true, the pulse width checks honor cell check  derate  fac-
       tors.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

